\t<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href="#p-search">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Copernicus" and "Kopernik" redirect here. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Copernicus_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Copernicus (disambiguation)">Copernicus (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class="infobox vcard" style="width:22em">\n<tr>\n<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold"><span class="fn">Nicolaus Copernicus</span></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;padding-bottom:0.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Nikolaus Kopernikus.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg/220px-Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg" width="220" height="256" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg/330px-Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f2/Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg/440px-Nikolaus_Kopernikus.jpg 2x" data-file-width="556" data-file-height="648" /></a>\n<div>The "Torun portrait" (anonymous, c. 1580), kept in <a href="/wiki/Toru%C5%84" title="Toru\xc5\x84">Toru\xc5\x84</a> town hall.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1">[1]</a></sup></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row">Born</th>\n<td><span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1473-02-19</span>)</span>19 February 1473<br />\n<span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Toru%C5%84" title="Toru\xc5\x84">Toru\xc5\x84 (Thorn)</a>, <a href="/wiki/Royal_Prussia" title="Royal Prussia">Royal Prussia</a>,<br />\n<a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Poland_(1385%E2%80%931569)" title="Kingdom of Poland (1385\xe2\x80\x931569)">Kingdom of Poland</a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row">Died</th>\n<td>24 May 1543<span style="display:none">(<span class="dday deathdate">1543-05-24</span>)</span> (aged&#160;70)<br />\n<span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Frombork" title="Frombork">Frombork (Frauenburg)</a>,<br />\n<a href="/wiki/Prince-Bishopric_of_Warmia" title="Prince-Bishopric of Warmia">Prince-Bishopric of Warmia</a>,<br />\nRoyal Prussia, Kingdom of<br />\nPoland</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row">Fields</th>\n<td class="category">\n<div class="hlist hlist-separated">\n<ul>\n<li>Astronomy</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Canon_law" title="Canon law">Canon law</a></li>\n<li>Economics</li>\n<li>Mathematics</li>\n<li>Medicine</li>\n<li>Politics</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row"><span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alma_mater" title="Alma mater">Alma mater</a></span></th>\n<td>\n<div class="plainlist nowrap">\n<ul>\n<li><a href="/wiki/Jagiellonian_University" title="Jagiellonian University">University of Krak\xc3\xb3w</a> (1491\xe2\x80\x934)</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/University_of_Bologna" title="University of Bologna">University of Bologna</a> (1496\xe2\x80\x931500)</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/University_of_Padua" title="University of Padua">University of Padua</a> (1501\xe2\x80\x933)</li>\n<li><a href="/wiki/University_of_Ferrara" title="University of Ferrara">University of Ferrara</a> (1503)</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row">Known&#160;for</th>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Heliocentrism" title="Heliocentrism">Heliocentrism</a><br />\n<a href="/wiki/Gresham%27s_Law" class="mw-redirect" title="Gresham\'s Law">Copernicus\' Law</a><br />\n<a href="/wiki/Copernican_principle" title="Copernican principle">Copernican principle</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row">Influences</th>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Aristarchus_of_Samos" title="Aristarchus of Samos">Aristarchus of Samos</a>, <a href="/wiki/Martianus_Capella" title="Martianus Capella">Martianus Capella</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th scope="row">Influenced</th>\n<td><a href="/wiki/Johannes_Kepler" title="Johannes Kepler">Johannes Kepler</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><b>Signature</b>\n<div style="padding-top:0.25em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_(podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika).svg" class="image" title="Nicolaus Copernicus\'s signature"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_%28podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika%29.svg/128px-Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_%28podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika%29.svg.png" width="128" height="41" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_%28podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika%29.svg/192px-Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_%28podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f1/Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_%28podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika%29.svg/256px-Nicolaus_Copernicus_signature_%28podpis_Miko%C5%82aja_Kopernika%29.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="645" data-file-height="205" /></a></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<table class="vertical-navbox nowraplinks plainlist" style="float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;font-size:88%">\n<tr>\n<td style="padding-top:0.4em;line-height:1.2em">Part of a series on</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style="padding:0.2em 0.4em 0.2em;padding-top:0;font-size:145%;line-height:1.2em"><a href="/wiki/Physical_cosmology" title="Physical cosmology">Physical</a> <a href="/wiki/Cosmology" title="Cosmology">cosmology</a></th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em"><a href="/wiki/File:Ilc_9yr_moll4096.png" class="image"><img alt="Full-sky image derived from nine years\' WMAP data" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3c/Ilc_9yr_moll4096.png/220px-Ilc_9yr_moll4096.png" width="220" height="110" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3c/Ilc_9yr_moll4096.png/330px-Ilc_9yr_moll4096.png 1.5x, //upload.wiki